SETUP THE SLIDE
Search for “Image Carousel” on the search widget tab. Then follow the setting below.

CONTENT TAB:
Image size: Full
Slides to Show: 3
Slides to Scroll: 1

STYLE TAB:
Make sure the Image Spacing is “0”

ADD CSS CODE TO WIDGET:
Go to Advanced Tab >> scroll to Custom CSS >>  then paste the code below: 

.swiper-slide .swiper-slide-inner img{
    transform: scale(0.8);
}

.swiper-slide.swiper-slide-next .swiper-slide-inner img{
    transform: scale(1);
}



